title: Bioobchod Rozmaryna
description: Large organic store stocking a wide range of products including: cold foods for takeaway like salads, meals, sandwiches, burgers, wheaty sticks; sweets like vegan chocolates and flap jacks; natural cosmetics; fresh organic vegetable. Located near metro station Anděl, bus station Na Kníažecí­, and train station Smíchovské Nádraíží­.
